title: How to Install a K&N Air Intake on 09-13 Chevy, GMC & Cadillac 6.2L, 5.3L and 4.8L
description: See just what goes into installing a free-flow K&N Air Intake on your 09-13 Chevy, GMC & Cadillac 6.2L, 5.3L and 4.8L Models.

asset.title: 2009-2013 Chevy, GMC & Cadillac Models 6.2L, 5.3L and 4.8L Air Intake Installation
asset.description: This K&N Blackhawk Induction™ air intake was designed for a selection of 2009, 2010, 2011 and 2013 Chevy, GMC & Cadillac models with 6.2L, 5.3L and 4.8L engines. K&N 71-3070 air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 12 horsepower at 5342 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. Discover how easy it is to install power-gaining performance on your 2009-2013 Chevy, GMC & Cadillac models with 6.2L, 5.3L and 4.8L engines.
